<p>
  On Windows, you can install Gosu through RubyGems:
  <br>
  <tt>gem install <strong>gosu</strong></tt>
  <br>
  <a style="display: inline-block" href="https://github.com/gosu/gosu/wiki/Getting-Started-on-OS-X">Installation instructions for macOS</a>
